latestPosts.caption: 2024, you’ve been so kind to me. A year full of blessings, growth and memories I’ll hold close to my heart. Walking into 2025 with a full heart and so much hope🤍

When your eyes are the life of the party this New Year’s Eve! ✨👁️ 

I’m turning heads with this ultra-glam eye look that’s all about bold strokes and seamless blends. 

Here’s the breakdown:
•Kay Beauty Eyeshadow Palette in ‘Outshine’
•24H Kajal Eyeliner Duo
•Lash Maximizer Mascara
	
Kept the base fresh and lips neutral to make sure the eyes do all the talking. 

Ready to ring in the New Year with this killer look🖤
